      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; independent code review completed.",
      "rationale": "Commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is version-controlled and has a documented QA history, but the hemolysis power-law sub-model has not undergone independent code review. Achieved level 2 against required level 4 for MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
