      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental dataset provides flow rate and pressure measurements but fluid temperature and exact hematocrit levels are incompletely documented, limiting boundary condition fidelity. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
