      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic comparison of hemolysis model forms (Giersiepen, Heuser-Opitz, modified power-law) with justification for selected form; turbulence model sensitivity documented.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law was selected without systematic comparison against alternative hemolysis model forms. k-omega SST turbulence model used without sensitivity analysis across turbulence closure options. Factor not assessed at required depth; achieved level 2 against required level 5."
    },
    {
